    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the rice is cooking, add your <strong>ground</strong> <strong>smoked paprika </strong>and<strong> cayenne pepper</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to a large bowl with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your<strong> Cajun-style seasoning</strong></p><p>Transfer <strong>half </strong>of the<strong> Cajun-style seasoning</strong> to a separate bowl and set aside (you'll use the rest later!)</p><p>Drain your <strong>king prawns</strong></p>",
