    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>chopped pepper </strong>and <strong>king prawns</strong> in the large bowl of Cajun-style seasoning and then thread them onto the<strong> skewers </strong>– these are your <strong>Cajun-style king prawn skewers</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>Cajun-style king prawn skewers </strong>to a <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined baking tray and put the tray in the oven for 12-15 min or until the prawns are cooked through and the peppers are tender</p>",
