      "instruction": "<p>While the skewers are cooking, chop your <strong>tomato[es] </strong>finely</p><p>Chop your <strong>coriander </strong>finely, including the stalks</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped tomato</strong> and <strong>white wine vinegar </strong>to a small bowl with the <strong>chopped coriander </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and mix to combine – this is your <strong>tomato salsa</strong></p>",
